                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The giant badger enters a state of pure rage that lasts for 1 minute, until there are no enemies it can perceive, or until it falls @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Unconscious]{Unconscious}, whichever comes first.</p>\n<p>While raging, the giant badger has AC 17, its jaws Strike deals 1d8+8 damage, and its claw Strike deals 1d6+6 damage. While raging, the giant badger also can't use actions that have the concentrate trait except for @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Seek]{Seek}.</p>\n<p>After it has stopped raging, a giant badger can't use Badger Rage again for 1 minute.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>@Compendium[pf2e.feature-effects.Effect: Rage]{Effect: Rage}</p>"
